dashboardQueries.name: fe0f9e84-7fe6-4c3a-978a-606604c904b1
dashboardQueries.query:
graph.metadata.vendor_name = "Cyware"
graph.metadata.product_name = "Cyware Intel Exchange"
$country = strings.coalesce(graph.entity.artifact.location.country_or_region, graph.entity.location.country_or_region)
$country != ""
$entityid = graph.metadata.product_entity_id
match:
    $country
outcome:
    $count = count_distinct($entityid)
order:
    $count desc
limit:
    15

dashboardQueries.name: 6e685abd-4840-4419-9ba6-d4b0782f01af
dashboardQueries.query:
graph.metadata.vendor_name = "Cyware"
graph.metadata.product_name = "Cyware Intel Exchange"

$score = graph.metadata.threat.risk_score
$entityid = graph.metadata.product_entity_id

$risk_category = if(graph.metadata.threat.risk_score = 0, "None", if(graph.metadata.threat.risk_score >= 1 and graph.metadata.threat.risk_score <= 29, "Low", if(graph.metadata.threat.risk_score >= 30 and graph.metadata.threat.risk_score <= 69, "Medium", if(graph.metadata.threat.risk_score >= 70, "High", "Unknown"))))
match:
    $risk_category
outcome:
    $count = count_distinct($entityid)
order:
    $count desc
limit:
    15

dashboardQueries.query:

graph.metadata.product_name = "Cyware Intel Exchange"

match:
    $date, $severity
outcome:
    $count=count_distinct($entityid)
order:
    $date asc
limit:
    10000
